 Marketing and public relations training  for small business and non-profits  





 Training your team   

 Markus MP, Inc. will train your staff, board and volunteers in marketing communications. We'll work on your strategic plan and
develop an easy to follow step-by-step action plan. We'll show you how to write press releases, e-marketing campaigns, blogs, social media posts, web
content, marketing materials, press kits, and how to develop mailing lists. We provide scripts,
templates and checklists to make your plan simple to implement and monitor, and to help keep your activities on track.   



 Marketing, public relations and special event materials  

 Let Markus MP make YOUR ideas reality. We will partner with your staff and volunteers
to create marketing, public relations and social media campaigns that enhance your organization’s professional image and reputation. We will also create your marketing materials, invitation, sponsorship packet and program booklets for your special events.   



 Business writing  

 Markus MP, Inc. takes care of your business writing needs, helping you share your news and fundraising messages with your
customers, vendors and staff.  Ask us about business communications, proposals, marketing
brochures, newsletters, e-mail campaigns, annual reports, grant applications, internal memos, etc. We're also your friendly efficient assistant for
your back office support services. 
 
Check out our affordable pricing.  



 

 


 









