 Crisis communications  

 Unexpected situations or disasters happen, but you need to concentrate on keeping your operations running. Every organization needs a crisis communications plan to help keep your funders, customers, vendors, staff – and the media – informed. Contact Markus MP to develop your unique plan that provides step-by-step training for your staff and
volunteers.  

 

 







 



