Overview


Markus, Inc. is a general contractor, builder, woodworker and carpenter that specializes in remodels and renovations, furniture builder, building repairs and furniture repairs.  The company also builds canoes and reproduces antique wooden boxes.
A new additional product line is a small weather tight 10' x 15' cabin, designed for remote locations that can be assembled in one weekend with minimal environmental impact.


